	%h4 Alerts
	%p Alerts are a simplified variant of cards for content that does not need a header or footer.
	.card.alert This is a default alert.
	%code.demo
		&lt;div class="card alert"&gt;This is a default alert.&lt/div&gt;

	%p Alerts can also be assigned a color scheme.
	.row
		.col-md-6.col-lg-4
			.card.alert.primary Primary message
